show.description: When Dhruva has to end his 10 year marriage contract with his Wife Swapna, he has to end many things which had stopped him to be on his own, why did he get into this contract marriage in first place and what surprise awaits him for all the sacrifice he has done for the past 10 years.watch  "The End of Us" only on KUKU TV.
